{{Infobox themed area
| image       = Gold Coast Parklands sign.JPG
| image_width = 220
| caption     = Original Gold Coast Parklands sign removed from venue in 2013 prior to demolition of complex.
| opened      = {{Start date|1988|12|07}}
| closed      = 2013
