==Personal life== He holds both [[Serbia]]n<ref name="FD"/> and Kosovo citizenship.
==Career== Born in [[Đakovica]], [[SFR Yugoslavia]], he moved with his family to Germany. Kadrijaj played youth football for [[FC Stern 1919 München]] and [[SpVgg Unterhaching]].<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.spvgg-unterhaching.de/club/player_detail.php3?player_id=3076|title=Profile|language=German|publisher=SpVgg Unterhaching}}</ref> He made his senior debut for SpVgg Unterhaching during the 2010–11 season.<ref name = "FD">{{fussballdaten|id=kadrijajvalonis|name=Valonis Kadrijaj}}</ref>
